{"tid":657071,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思益廣]大家平時睇開咩時裝資訊網?","createTime":"2018-05-07T19:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T12:35:42.000Z","uid":16562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"de58970aecfbfdb4bd39c8b77c6582f3965367fa","tid":657071,"uid":16562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T19:39:18.000Z","msg":"是咁的, 小弟想改改自己只係一味著淨色TEE+條米色/黑藍色長褲既style<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但落街行衫鋪又冇乜idea 想約frd出黎襯衫又約唔到(太毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n於是我諗住睇下啲時裝資訊網(<a href=\"http://類似講科技既unwire.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E9%A1%9E%E4%BC%BC%E8%AC%9B%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E6%97%A2unwire.hk&d=ltR1ESwHDkZv1QxYodHvaXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=1cc99f2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">類似講科技既unwire.hk</a>或者講電話既Ringhk)<br />\n<br />\n大家有冇邊個網推薦下咁? 最好有得睇埋呢期興著咩style咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講到最後我只係想做返啲野脫毒姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce221916e1c2a6933c4f2e2778083062951b5e75","tid":657071,"uid":15112,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T19:45:58.000Z","msg":"有個app 叫 WEAR<br />\n都幾多人post 啲衣著上去<br />\n可以睇睇作參考"},{"pid":"71a053d7fd2a5f4d9a0a6566cbe98c39bd79e3e1","tid":657071,"uid":16562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce221916e1c2a6933c4f2e2778083062951b5e75","tid":657071,"uid":15112,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime